{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/union-find/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Kooku's log","author":"Kooku","siteUrl":"https://kooku.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"koomg9599/kooku-s-log"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"kooku"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b83c56a8-21f8-5546-8e5d-e1195bf9b8c8","excerpt":"이번 카카오 인턴 코딩테스트에서 유니온 파인드 알고리즘이 나와서 정리하였다. 내 생각 : 매우매우 유용한(?) 알고리즘이다.  유니온 파인드(Union Find)란? 정의 유니온 파인드(Union Find) : 서로소 집합(Disjoint Set) 그리고 병합 찾기 집합(Merge Find Set…","html":"<p>이번 카카오 인턴 코딩테스트에서 유니온 파인드 알고리즘이 나와서 정리하였다.</p>\n<p><em>내 생각</em> : 매우매우 유용한(?) 알고리즘이다. </p>\n<h2 id=\"유니온-파인드union-find란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9C%A0%EB%8B%88%EC%98%A8-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%B8%EB%93%9Cunion-find%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"유니온 파인드union find란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>유니온 파인드(Union Find)란?</h2>\n<h4 id=\"정의\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EC%9D%98\" aria-label=\"정의 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>정의</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>유니온 파인드(Union Find) : 서로소 집합(Disjoint Set) 그리고 병합 찾기 집합(Merge Find Set)이라고도 불리며 여러 서로소 집합의 정보를 저장하고 있는 자료구조를 의미합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"예시\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"예시 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>예시</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>다음 아래와 같이 원소들이 있다고 가정을 했을 때</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8.783783783783782%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAUUlEQVQI1y3OiwpAUBCE4XEpJHSU20EU5f3f0C+z9bVb204rSbP+mjAiQUSPHDtqlDhRoPGcocOK1PfaHPj1xYsDgwNvtKhwOTjg8T74gS88vs8dArX262L8AAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"/static/8feae15fc318943d78a3f08a1a1e948d/fcda8/union-find-01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8feae15fc318943d78a3f08a1a1e948d/12f09/union-find-01.png 148w,\n/static/8feae15fc318943d78a3f08a1a1e948d/e4a3f/union-find-01.png 295w,\n/static/8feae15fc318943d78a3f08a1a1e948d/fcda8/union-find-01.png 590w,\n/static/8feae15fc318943d78a3f08a1a1e948d/37523/union-find-01.png 720w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>각각의 원소들이 어떤 원소들과 연결이 되어있는지 입력을 받는다고 가정하면(1-2, 2-5, 5-6, 5-8, 3-4 이런 방식으로) 아래와 같이 3개의 서로소 집합이 나올 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8.783783783783782%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAVElEQVQI103O2wpAUBCF4aWEzQUSciwX8v5v6J+sC1Nfzd41a0aSFhQYMLvf0aLGiYQeF3JUnuswYdRX0etA6c/1FxgLGtwOjPfjwOS5WLI5PIuDXtwWAtZco3X0AAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"/static/f39d95e4e128c09a40c5b4272fe5ba5e/fcda8/union-find-02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f39d95e4e128c09a40c5b4272fe5ba5e/12f09/union-find-02.png 148w,\n/static/f39d95e4e128c09a40c5b4272fe5ba5e/e4a3f/union-find-02.png 295w,\n/static/f39d95e4e128c09a40c5b4272fe5ba5e/fcda8/union-find-02.png 590w,\n/static/f39d95e4e128c09a40c5b4272fe5ba5e/37523/union-find-02.png 720w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"구현\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84\" aria-label=\"구현 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>구현</h2>\n<h4 id=\"원리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9B%90%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"원리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>원리</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>배열을 이용해서 Tree 자료구조를 만들어 구현하며 위에 나와 있는 <code class=\"language-text\">{1, 2, 5, 6, 8}, {3, 4}, {7}</code>의 경우에는 아래처럼 표현 및 구현이 가능합니다.</li>\n<li>즉, 최상단 노드인 Root노드를 집합을 구분하는 ID처럼 생각하면 이해가 더 편합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.72972972972973%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"/static/b1f67ff1955dc8089733c52d9fc7c132/fcda8/union-find-03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b1f67ff1955dc8089733c52d9fc7c132/12f09/union-find-03.png 148w,\n/static/b1f67ff1955dc8089733c52d9fc7c132/e4a3f/union-find-03.png 295w,\n/static/b1f67ff1955dc8089733c52d9fc7c132/fcda8/union-find-03.png 590w,\n/static/b1f67ff1955dc8089733c52d9fc7c132/d67ca/union-find-03.png 714w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>주어진 두 원소 또는 집합을 합하는 <code class=\"language-text\">Union</code>부분과 원소가 어떤 집합에 있는지 찾는 <code class=\"language-text\">Find</code>함수로 이루어져있다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">parent[i]</code> : 원소 <code class=\"language-text\">i</code>의 부모 노드를 가지고 있는 배열, <code class=\"language-text\">parent[i]</code>는 <code class=\"language-text\">i</code>의 부모 노드</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"예시-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%88%EC%8B%9C-1\" aria-label=\"예시 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>예시</h2>\n<p>이 문제 한번만 풀어보면 완벽히 이해할듯 싶다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>집합의 표현</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.acmicpc.net/problem/1717\">https://www.acmicpc.net/problem/1717</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c++\"><pre class=\"language-c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\n#include &lt;vector&gt;\n\nusing namespace std;\n\nvector&lt;int&gt; parent(1000010, -1);\n\nint find(int a) {\n\tif (parent[a] == -1) return parent[a] = a;\n\tif (parent[a] == a) return a;\n\telse return parent[a] = find(parent[a]);\n}\n\nvoid setParent(int a, int b) {\n\tint rootA = find(a);\n\tint rootB = find(b);\n\tparent[rootA] = rootB;\n}\n\nint main() {\n\tios_base::sync_with_stdio(false); cin.tie(NULL); cout.tie(NULL);\n\tint n, m;\n\tcin &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; m;\n\t\n\tint a, b, c;\n\tfor (int i = 0; i &lt; m; i++) {\n\t\tcin &gt;&gt; a &gt;&gt; b &gt;&gt; c;\n\t\tif (a == 0) {\n\t\t\tsetParent(b, c);\n\t\t}\n\t\telse {\n\t\t\tif (find(b) == find(c)) cout &lt;&lt; &quot;YES&quot; &lt;&lt; &quot;\\n&quot;;\n\t\t\telse cout &lt;&lt; &quot;NO&quot; &lt;&lt; &quot;\\n&quot;;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\treturn 0;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://twpower.github.io/115-union-find-disjoint-set\">[Algorithm] 유니온 파인드(Union Find)와 서로소 집합(Disjoint Set) :: twpower</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"union-find","date":"November 10, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/union-find/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/data mining/hopfield-network/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Hopfield Network","category":"data mining"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/web/http1.1-vs-http2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"HTTP/1.1 vs HTTP/2","category":"web"}}}}}